nodes.text: "Wookiee" was the name of a file that the Alliance to Restore the Republic-owned BRT supercomputer Mistress Mnemos utilized by 1 ABY on the planet Fusai. Presumably, it contained details on the Wookiees, who had acted as allies of the Rebel Alliance during the Galactic Civil War. It possessed at least one section, OC-356, which gave details on Chewbacca, a Rebel Alliance member, although it lacked information on the specific relationship between Han Solo and Chewbacca, or the circumstances behind their meeting, which led to it asking C-3PO for these details, who denied knowing anything as he wasn't present at the time.
